0xD1D31681// SetVisualSettingFloat
void SET_VISUAL_SETTING_FLOAT(char* name, float value);Parameters:name: The name of the value to set, such as pedLight.color.red.value: The value to write.Overrides a floating point value from visualsettings.dat temporarily.
